are you?

8
00:00:14,815 --> 00:00:16,048
I'm Bruce's friend.

9
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:17,582
And you're a piece
of gutter trash.

10
00:00:17,584 --> 00:00:18,984
You think that
little minx is

11
00:00:18,986 --> 00:00:20,218
gonna tell you
something, do you?

12
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:21,553
Getting information
out of a girl

13
00:00:21,555 --> 00:00:23,355
like that requires
a level of deception

14
00:00:23,357 --> 00:00:24,956
that you do not yet possess.

15
00:00:24,958 --> 00:00:26,191
GORDON:
<i>You're under arrest.</i>

16
00:00:26,193 --> 00:00:28,627
May I ask what
the charge is?

17
00:00:28,629 --> 00:00:30,862
The kidnapping and torture
of Aubrey James.

18
00:00:30,864 --> 00:00:32,331
These were Ms. Kringle's.

19
00:00:32,333 --> 00:00:35,100
A man with nothing
to love is free.

20
00:00:35,102 --> 00:00:37,502
Hey, Parks,
you did good today.

21
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:40,739
THOMPKINS:<i> Eduardo Flamingo</i>
<i>killed Officer Parks</i>

22
00:00:40,741 --> 00:00:43,308
