perhaps?

47
00:02:25,579 --> 00:02:27,546
You're here to gloat.

48
00:02:27,548 --> 00:02:31,416
Does the name Katherine Parks
mean anything to you?

49
00:02:33,053 --> 00:02:35,654
No, can't say it does.

50
00:02:35,656 --> 00:02:39,558
I'm gonna be there tomorrow.

51
00:02:40,694 --> 00:02:43,728
I'm gonna watch them
put you away.

52
00:02:43,730 --> 00:02:44,930
(chuckles softly)

53
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,800
Always a pleasure, Detective.

54
00:02:48,802 --> 00:02:50,769
(door buzzes, opens)

55
