Hey.

56
00:02:58,011 --> 00:02:59,678
Hey.

57
00:03:01,181 --> 00:03:03,181
(thunder rumbling)

58
00:03:03,183 --> 00:03:06,751
You're soaking wet.

59
00:03:09,056 --> 00:03:12,123
Do you want to talk about it?

60
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:14,993
Katherine Parks was 23.

61
00:03:16,997 --> 00:03:20,232
On the force a year.

62
00:03:20,234 --> 00:03:23,101
And today we put her
in the ground

63
00:03:23,103 --> 00:03:25,237
because when I had the chance,

64
00:03:25,239 --> 00:03:27,672
