her family?

75
00:03:51,632 --> 00:03:53,698
(sighs)

76
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:57,002
I went to see Galavan today.

77
00:03:57,004 --> 00:03:58,904
And?
You're asking

78
00:03:58,906 --> 00:04:01,773
did I get the guards to
turn the cameras off? No.

79
00:04:01,775 --> 00:04:03,909
But they would have.

80
00:04:03,911 --> 00:04:07,112
Galavan as good as killed Parks,
Essen and a dozen other cops,

81
00:04:07,114 --> 00:04:08,847
and yet he sits there,

82
00:04:08,849 --> 00:04:11,082
smiling, breathing.

83
00:04:11,084 --> 00:04:14,586
And tomorrow, Aubrey James is
going in front of the grand jury

84
00:04:14,588 --> 00:04:16,054
and telling them
that he was kidnapped

85
00:04:16,056 --> 00:04:17,055
and tortured by Galavan.

86
00:04:17,057 --> 00:04:18,657
He's gonna be put away

87
00:04:18,659 --> 00:04:20,625
for a long time.
Maybe.

88
00:04:21,995 --> 00:04:24,429
Just the way he acted.

89
00:04:24,431 --> 00:04:27,065
It wasn't a man
looking at a decade in prison.

90
00:04:28,669 --> 00:04:30,502
I have a bad feeling.

91
00:04:30,504 --> 00:04:32,537
Jim, it's over.

92
00:04:32,539 --> 00:04:34,940
You did good.

93
00:04:36,843 --> 00:04:38,443
Now, come to bed.

94
00:04:38,445 --> 00:04:39,778
Doctor's orders.

95
00:04:50,324 --> 00:04:52,524
