97
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:06,004
MAN:
Where am I?

98
00:05:06,006 --> 00:05:07,739
Who are you?

99
00:05:07,741 --> 00:05:09,774
The day of reckoning is at hand.

100
00:05:09,776 --> 00:05:12,410
