110
00:05:40,007 --> 00:05:42,507
She'll see through you.
Or her uncle will.

111
00:05:42,509 --> 00:05:44,075
Well, that's very possible.

112
00:05:44,077 --> 00:05:45,777
And?

113
00:05:45,779 --> 00:05:47,278
Bruce,

114
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,747
they're playing nice with you

115
00:05:48,749 --> 00:05:50,949
because they think
you trust them.

116
00:05:50,951 --> 00:05:54,185
Once they see you don't,
it'll get ugly fast.

117
00:05:54,187 --> 00:05:56,955
Your logic is flawless, Selina.
It's not too late...

118
00:05:56,957 --> 00:05:58,490
If there's even a chance
Galavan knows

119
00:05:58,492 --> 00:06:00,125
who killed my parents,
I have to take it.

120
00:06:01,695 --> 00:06:04,029
I told Alfred I have
fencing practice after school

121
00:06:04,031 --> 00:06:06,331
to buy us some time
if we need it.

122
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:07,532
Hey.

123
00:06:08,535 --> 00:06:11,169
The best liars
always tell the truth.

124
00:06:11,171 --> 00:06:13,304
Something to remember.

125
00:06:13,306 --> 00:06:14,873
Thank you.

126
00:06:17,778 --> 00:06:20,078
That's her car. You'd b...

127
00:06:21,415 --> 00:06:22,947
(car door closes)

128
00:06:27,187 --> 00:06:28,853
Alvarez, call the morgue.

129
00:06:28,855 --> 00:06:31,022
See if any bodies turned up
matching Gertrude Cobblepot.

130
00:06:31,024 --> 00:06:33,491
She didn't just vanish;
Galavan killed her.

131
00:06:33,493 --> 00:06:34,859
Did that yesterday.

132
00:06:34,861 --> 00:06:37,195
And you're gonna
do it again today.

133
00:06:37,197 --> 00:06:38,930
I got my own cases, Gordon.

134
00:06:38,932 --> 00:06:41,266
Turn up anything on that symbol
we found in the penthouse?

135
00:06:41,268 --> 00:06:44,469
No. I'm waiting for Father Mike
up at St. Bart's.

136
00:06:44,471 --> 00:06:46,104
Sent him a picture
of the cassock, too.

137
00:06:46,106 --> 00:06:48,173
He's up on all that
religious mumbo-jumbo.

138
00:06:48,175 --> 00:06:51,009
What exactly
are we after here?

139
00:06:51,011 --> 00:06:52,844
Something tying Galavan
to the murders of Essen,

140
00:06:52,846 --> 00:06:54,412
Parks, any of the
people he killed.

141
00:06:54,414 --> 00:06:58,016
Not to state the obvious, Jim,
but the guy's going to jail.

142
00:06:58,018 --> 00:07:00,618
I went to see him last night.
Yeah?

143
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:02,487
