a massage parlor.

228
00:11:38,631 --> 00:11:40,865
Maybe there's
another entrance.

229
00:11:40,867 --> 00:11:43,434
(women screaming)

230
00:11:51,077 --> 00:11:52,744
GORDON:
Get these girls out of here.

231
00:11:52,746 --> 00:11:55,546
Come on, come on. Come on.

232
00:11:58,785 --> 00:12:00,985
GCPD!

